 Report]] |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/14207 |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQuBC1Is?url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/14207/metroid-prime-3-corruption-preview-on-wii-shop-channel |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 日本地区为9月20日，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/vc_sme/ |title=VC スーパーメトロイド |language=ja |publisher=Nintendo |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQu6FHeO?url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/vc_sme/ |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 欧洲地区为10月12日。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Super-Nintendo/Super-Metroid-279613.html |title=Virtual Console: Super Metroid |publisher=Nintendo of Europe |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQuFQj3a?url=https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Super-Nintendo/Super-Metroid-279613.html |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 
