 |date=2006-07-11 |author=Mike, Major |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081016085743/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/72550/15-retro-games-for-the-wii-you-must-play/ |archivedate=2008-10-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 《超级银河战士》被列为《[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]》长期超级任天堂最佳游戏第一位，击败了第二位《[[时空之轮|时空之轮]]》和第三位《[[塞尔达传说_众神的三角力量|塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量]]》。<ref>{{cite web | accessdate=2013-01-16 | url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-snes-games-all-time/ | title=Best Super Nintendo games of all time | publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] | date=2012-04-17 | author=GamesRadar staff | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvUzNmF?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-snes-games-all-time/ | archivedate=2015-05-11 | deadurl=no }}</ref> 超级银河战士同样被[[ScrewAttack|ScrewAttack]]命名为长期最佳游戏，击败第二位《[[塞尔达传说_众神的三角力量|塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量]]》和第三位《[[最终幻想VI|最终幻想VI]]》。<ref>{{cite web | accessdate=2013-01-31 | url=http://www.screwattack.com/shows/originals/screwattack-top-10s/top-20-snes-games-10-1 | title=Top 20 SNES Games | publisher=''[[ScrewAttack|ScrewAttack]]'' | date=2011-08-15 | author=Craig Skistimas | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121123093947/http://www.screwattack.com/shows/originals/screwattack-top-10s/top-20-snes-games-10-1 | archivedate=2012-11-23 }}</ref> [[经典游戏室|经典游戏室]]的CGR Undertow系列同样也将超级银河战士列为长期最佳游戏，击败了第二位《[[塞尔达传说_众神的三角力量|塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量]]》和第三位《[[超級瑪利歐世界|超級瑪利歐世界]]》。<ref>{{cite web | accessdate=2013-02-05 | url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzHaCksTOo8 | title=CGRundertow Top 20 SNES Games Part Four | publisher=[[Classic_Game_Room|Classic Game Room]] | author=Classic Game Room's Derek and Kevin | date=2011-09-10 | archive-date=2020-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630152343/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzHaCksTOo8 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》将超级银河战士列为银河战士系列最佳一作，击败了第二位《[[银河战士Prime|银河战士Prime]]》和第三位《[[银河战士_零点任务|银河战士 零点任务]]》<ref>{{cite journal | journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] | title=Ultimate Metroid | volume=259 | page=73 | author=Nintendo Power staff | date=October 2010}}</ref>

==影响==
在《超级银河战士》发行之后的八年内，没有新的后续系列游戏发行。银河战士系列再也没有取得与[[瑪利歐系列|瑪利歐系列]]和[[薩爾達傳說系列|薩爾達傳說系列]]同样成就。<ref name=gr-history />制作前两作银河战士的横井军平在[[Virtual_Boy|Virtual Boy]]銷售慘淡失败之后，离开了任天堂公司。并且于1997年在一场车祸中去世。<ref name=gr-history /><ref name="ign-history">{{cite web|author=Rus McLaughlin|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/08/15/ign-presents-the-history-of-metroid|title=IGN Presents The History of Metroid|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=2007-08-24|accessdate=2008-02-17|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvpWIH2?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/08/15/ign-presents-the-history-of-metroid|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Varney |first=Allen |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/issues/issue_87/490-Searching-for-Gunpei-Yokoi.3 |title=The Escapist: Searching for Gunpei Yokoi |publisher=[[Defy_Media|Defy Media]] |work=[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|The Escapist]] |page=3 |date=2007-03-06 |accessdate=2014-12-31 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvtsNSQ?url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/issues/issue_87/490-Searching-for-Gunpei-Yokoi.3 |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1997/10/07/game-boy-inventor-dies-in-car-crash|title=Game Boy Inventor Dies in Car Crash|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=1997-10-07|accessdate=2014-12-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvyVN6d?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1997/10/07/game-boy-inventor-dies-in-car-crash|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref> 在本系列的间断期，游戏迷们期望能有一款[[任天堂64|N64]]的银河战士游戏。<ref name="ign-history"/> 坂本曾考虑制作一版N64的游戏，但没有引起兴趣，主要是因为N64的控制手柄。任天堂寻求其它公司能够制作N64的银河战士游戏，但此提议被否决。由于制作方认为他们无法制作一款与超级银河战士同样高度的作品。<ref>{{cite web |title=Yoshio Sakamoto discusses Metroid 64, Metroid Dread and the 3DS |url=http://www.gamestm.co.uk/features/yoshio-sakamoto-discusses-metroid-64-metroid-dread-and-the-unwritten-future-of-the-warioware-series/ |work=[[GamesTM|GamesTM]] |date=2010-09-14 |accessdate=2013-12-31 |archive-date=2018-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127225151/https://www.gamestm.co.uk/features/yoshio-sakamoto-discusses-metroid-64-metroid-dread-and-the-unwritten-future-of-the-warioware-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[宫本茂|宫本茂]]认为任天堂无法在N64出现具体的想法。<ref name="roundtable">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/11/15/metroid-prime-roundtable-qa|title=Metroid Prime Roundtable QA|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=2002-11-15|accessdate=2008-02-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQw4UNiV?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/11/15/metroid-prime-roundtable-qa|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref> 超级银河战士的合作伙伴[[Intelligent_Systems|Intelligent Systems]]考虑在[[Game_Boy_Color|Game Boy Color]]继续创作一款系列游戏，但是由于手持设备的技术局限，想法被搁浅。<ref name=gr-history />

2002年，任天堂在[[GameCube|GameCube]]和[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]发行了两款新的银河战士系列游戏，分别为《[[银河战士Prime|银河战士Prime]]》和《[[银河战士_融合|银河战士 融合]]》，此举标志着本系列游戏在八年间断后重新出现。<ref name=gr-history /><ref name="ign-history"/>《银河战士Prime》是第一款3D游戏，由[[Retro_Studios|Retro Studios]]<ref name="roundtable" />制作，它是一个在得克萨斯州奥斯汀新成立的第二方游戏制作公司。<ref name=road>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041217081949/http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/november02/metroidconf/index.shtml|url=http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/november02/metroidconf/index.shtml|title=The Road to Metroid Prime|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|date=2002-11-12|archivedate=2004-12-17|accessdate=2012-10-05|first=Raymond|last=Padilla|deadurl=yes}}</ref>《Prime》是一个以第一人称视角的动作探险类游戏，<ref name="fpa">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/24/metroid-a-first-person-adventure|title=Metroid a First Person Adventure?|date=2001-02-23|author=IGN Staff|accessdate=2011-07-25|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQw8rpJa?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/24/metroid-a-first-person-adventure|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>变成变形球后会转为第三人称。<ref name="gamespot-metroid-prime">{{cite web|authorlink=Greg Kasavin|last=Kasavin|first=Greg|title=Metroid Prime review|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2002-11-15|url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/metroid-prime-review/1900-2897768/|accessdate=2014-01-19|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwCudqE?url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/metroid-prime-review/1900-2897768/|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>《银河战士 融合》是一个2D横向卷轴游戏，由同样先前制作《超级银河战士》的任天堂开发一部制作，在视觉上与融合具有相似之处。<ref name="ign-handson">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-04 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/08/22/metroid-fusion-hands-on |title=Metroid Fusion Hands-on |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2002-08-22 |first=Craig |last=Harris |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwKL8x1?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/08/22/metroid-fusion-hands-on |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>它的剧情、屏幕视角以及控制都模仿《超级银河战士》，<ref name="ign-handson"/>但由于此作注重故事情节，融合与先前的银河战士作品相比，更以线性方式展现，<ref name="ign-history" /><ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-04 |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/preview/3435 |title=Metroid Fusion |publisher=Nintendo World Report |date=2002-08-26 |last=Lake |first=Max |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwQXgLs?url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/preview/3435/metroid-fusion-game-boy-advance |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 此作更是第一款具有动画剪辑场景的2D银河战士。游戏的故事是通过文字和视觉的特写镜头展现。<ref name="ign-handson" />《Prime》和《融合》收到多方评价，<ref name=gr-history />并且与前作赢得多个年度大奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cube.gamespy.com/gamecube/metroid-prime/535883p1.html|title=Metroid Prime Bundle Announced|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|date=2004-08-04|accessdate=2010-07-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwOf5Dx?url=http://cube.gamespy.com/gamecube/metroid-prime/535883p1.html|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=yes}}</ref>在《银河战士 Prime》之后，三个第一人称游戏以及一个弹珠台游戏发行，其中包括它的后作《[[银河战士Prime_2_黑暗回音|银河战士Prime 2 黑暗回音]]》。<ref name=gr-history /><ref name="ign-history" />

由于《超级银河战士》按照完成游戏的时长给予玩家奖励，所以它成为了挑战[[競速破關|快速通关]]的一个人气之选。在这种玩法下，玩家们之间竞争谁能更快通关。<ref name="ign-history"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1504116/for-some-gamers-merely-finishing-a-game-isnt-enough/ |title=For Some Gamers, Merely Finishing A Game Isn't Enough |publisher=[[Viacom_International|Viacom International]] |work=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |first=Stephen |last=Totilo |date=2005-06-14 |accessdate=2009-01-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwY2RlZ?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1504116/for-some-gamers-merely-finishing-a-game-isnt-enough/ |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>《超级银河战士》和[[科乐美|科乐美]]1997年发行的《[[惡魔城X_月下夜想曲|惡魔城X 月下夜想曲]]》奠定了“[[银河恶魔城游戏|银河战士恶魔城]]”这一游戏类型。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/237119/Video_Koji_Igarashi_explores_what_makes_a_Metroidvania_game.php |title=Video: Koji Igarashi explores what makes a Metroidvania game |date=2015-02-23 |accessdate=2015-03-25 |publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |archive-date=2015-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318024648/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/237119/Video_Koji_Igarashi_explores_what_makes_a_Metroidvania_game.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/236410/The_undying_allure_of_the_Metroidvania.php |title=The undying allure of the Metroidvania |first=Christian |last=Nutt |date=2015-02-13 |accessdate=2015-03-23 |publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwkEUvl?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/236410/The_undying_allure_of_the_Metroidvania.php |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>本作给予了其他[[银河恶魔城游戏|银河战士恶魔城]]游戏启发，例如《[[Shadow_Complex|Shadow Complex]]》、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4119/making_shadow_complex_donald_.php |title=Making Shadow Complex: Donald Mustard Speaks |first=Christan |last=Nutt |date=2009-08-28 |accessdate=2009-08-28 |publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwoGKoy?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4119/making_shadow_complex_donald_.php |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 《[[The_Swapper|The Swapper]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/25/the-swapper-captures-the-essence-of-super-metroid|title=The Swapper Captures the Essence of Super Metroid|first=Marty|last=Sliva|date=2013-03-25|accessdate=2014-12-31|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwr3H5g?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/25/the-swapper-captures-the-essence-of-super-metroid|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref> 和《[[Axiom_Verge|Axiom Verge]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/game-dev-recipes-axiom-verge|title=Game Dev Recipes: Axiom Verge|first=Tom|last=McShea|work=USGamer|publisher=Gamer Network|date=2014-09-19|accessdate=2015-02-21|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwvVSfn?url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/game-dev-recipes-axiom-verge|archivedate=2015-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>游戏爱好者们还发布了几个自制的破解版超级银河战士ROM，里面包含了一些原游戏没有的新功能。<ref name="Hacking">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/196769/why_super_metroids_hacking_.php?page=4 |title=Why Super Metroid's Hacking Community is Still Going Strong |page=4 |first=Victoria |last=Earl |date=2013-07-27 |accessdate=2015-03-23 |publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQwzPRnW?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/196769/why_super_metroids_hacking_.php?page=4 |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>由drewseph在2006年制作的《超级银河战士 ''Redesign''》以新的道具，更大的探索区域和改良的物理引擎为特色。<ref name="Hacking" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vintagecomputing.com/index.php/archives/163 |title=Hacksterpiece Theatre: Return to Zebes with Super Metroid Redesign |work=Vintage Computers and Gaming |date=2006-09-05 |accessdate=2015-03-23 |first=Benj |last=Edwards |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQx2twbl?url=http://www.vintagecomputing.com/index.php/archives/163 |archivedate=2015-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow/story/293770/10-classic-video-game-hacks-everyone-should-play/10 |title=10 Classic Video Game Hacks Everyone Should Play |work=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]] |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2012-02-03 |accessdate=2015-03-23 |first=Benj |last=Edwards |archive-date=2016-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116181033/http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow/story/293770/10-classic-video-game-hacks-everyone-should-play/10 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2011年，一位名为SB的日本黑客发布了一个名为《银河战士：超级零点任务》的破解ROM，它意图将《超级银河战士》与后来发布的《银河战士：零点任务》的元素结合到一起。<ref name="Hacking" />

